The '''Compeer''' was the title for the overall head of the [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] crime organization known as the [[Exchange]]. Although details of the Compeer's powers are sketchy it can be suggested that, considering the power of the Compeer's under-bosses, such as [[G0-T0]] and [[Davik Kang]], that it was immense.

